---
import "@fontsource-variable/mona-sans/wght.css";
import LifecycleAccordion from "../components/LifecycleAccordion.astro";
import "../styles/global.css";

const repositoryUrl = "https://github.com/hussainph/volli-code";
const downloadUrl = `${repositoryUrl}/releases/latest`;
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Volli brings planning, orchestration, terminal agent execution, and review into one programmable workspace."
    />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a0a" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/volli-icon-dark.png" />
    <title>Volli Code | Program the software lifecycle</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main id="top">
      <section class="hero-shell" aria-label="Volli product demo">
        <div class="hero-placeholder">
          <div class="hero-brand">
            <img src="/volli-icon-dark.png" alt="" width="42" height="42" />
            <span>Volli</span>
          </div>

          <span class="play-mark" aria-hidden="true">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="20" height="20">
              <path d="M8.25 5.4v13.2L18.6 12 8.25 5.4Z" fill="currentColor" />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="statement-section">
        <div class="statement-grid">
          <div class="accordion-column">
            <LifecycleAccordion />
          </div>

          <div class="statement-copy">
            <h1><span>The ticket is</span> the workspace.</h1>

            <div class="body-copy">
              <p>
                I built Volli because coding agents can do the work, but the tools around them still
                split planning from execution. Volli brings both into one place: every ticket gets
                its own branch, terminal workspace, and as many agentic sessions as the work needs.
              </p>
              <p>
                The board turns your software lifecycle into a programmable system, with prompts
                and automations that run as work enters each phase. Every agent can use the Volli
                CLI to read the plan, create follow-up work, schedule tasks, and keep the project
                moving.
              </p>
              <p>
                Volli is open source, local-first, and built around your workflow instead of one
                agent provider. Use Claude Code, Codex, OpenCode, or any CLI harness with the same
                plan, lifecycle, and history.
              </p>
            </div>

            <div class="cta-row">
              <a class="cta cta-primary" href={downloadUrl}>
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="17" height="17" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path
                    fill="currentColor"
                    d="M17.05 20.28c-.98.95-2.05.8-3.08.35-1.09-.46-2.09-.48-3.24 0-1.44.62-2.2.44-3.06-.35C2.79 15.25 3.51 7.59 9.05 7.31c1.35.07 2.29.74 3.08.79 1.18-.24 2.31-.93 3.57-.84 1.51.12 2.65.72 3.4 1.8-3.12 1.87-2.38 5.98.48 7.13-.57 1.5-1.31 2.99-2.53 4.1v-.01ZM12.03 7.25C11.88 5.02 13.69 3.18 15.77 3c.29 2.58-2.34 4.5-3.74 4.25Z"
                  />
                </svg>
                <span>Download for macOS</span>
                <span class="keycap" aria-hidden="true">D</span>
              </a>
              <a class="cta cta-secondary" href={repositoryUrl}>
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" width="17" height="17" aria-hidden="true">
                  <path
                    fill="currentColor"
                    d="M12 .7a11.5 11.5 0 0 0-3.64 22.4c.58.1.79-.25.79-.56v-2.23c-3.22.7-3.9-1.37-3.9-1.37-.52-1.34-1.28-1.69-1.28-1.69-1.05-.72.08-.7.08-.7 1.16.08 1.77 1.19 1.77 1.19 1.03 1.77 2.71 1.26 3.37.96.1-.75.4-1.26.74-1.55-2.57-.29-5.27-1.28-5.27-5.69 0-1.26.45-2.28 1.19-3.09-.12-.29-.52-1.46.11-3.05 0 0 .97-.31 3.16 1.18a10.9 10.9 0 0 1 5.76 0c2.2-1.49 3.16-1.18 3.16-1.18.63 1.59.23 2.76.11 3.05.74.81 1.19 1.83 1.19 3.09 0 4.42-2.71 5.39-5.29 5.68.42.36.79 1.07.79 2.16v3.2c0 .31.21.67.8.56A11.5 11.5 0 0 0 12 .7Z"
                  />
                </svg>
                <span>Star on GitHub</span>
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <a class="footer-brand" href="#top" aria-label="Volli home">
        <img src="/volli-icon-dark.png" alt="" width="34" height="34" />
        <span>Volli</span>
      </a>
      <nav aria-label="Footer">
        <a href={repositoryUrl}>GitHub</a>
        <a href={`${repositoryUrl}#readme`}>Readme</a>
      </nav>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
